General.Name: PolyPlank publ AB
General.Description: PolyPlank AB (publ) engages in the manufacture and sale of recyclable products from recycled plastic and wood fiber waste in Sweden. The company offers terrace dividers, screening, and fences; balconies and access galleries; and sheds for garbage bins or bicycle storage for building, private, and municipal real estate companies. It also provides noise reduction systems for transport administration, real estate companies, industrial companies, municipalities, and construction companies; terrace profiles under the BeachPlank name; and core plugs for loading and shipping protection in paper bales. The company was incorporated in 1994 and is based in Färjestaden, Sweden.
